861
00:52:52.604 --> 00:52:54.780
which is essentially this.

862
00:52:54.823 --> 00:52:59.306
People will avoid
an action or an experience

863
00:52:59.350 --> 00:53:00.786
in proportion to how much

864
00:53:00.829 --> 00:53:03.484
it threatens their identity
and their world view.

865
00:53:03.528 --> 00:53:06.444
And the interesting thing
about Manson's Law of Avoidance

866
00:53:06.487 --> 00:53:10.970
